.TH "tomoyo_mkdev_perm" 9 "tomoyo_mkdev_perm" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tomoyo_mkdev_perm \- Check permission for "mkblock" and "mkchar".
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" tomoyo_mkdev_perm
.BI "(const u8 operation "  ","
.BI "const struct path *path "  ","
.BI "const unsigned int mode "  ","
.BI "unsigned int dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "operation" 12
Type of operation. (TOMOYO_TYPE_MKCHAR or TOMOYO_TYPE_MKBLOCK)
.IP "path" 12
Pointer to "struct path".
.IP "mode" 12
Create mode.
.IP "dev" 12
Device number.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 0 on success, negative value otherwise.
